<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Account Deletion Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .warning-icon {
      font-size: 48px;
      color: #dc3545;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .otp-code {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545, #c82333);
      color: white;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    }
    .warning-box {
      background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.3);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="warning-icon">⚠️</div>
      <h1 style="color: #dc3545; margin: 0;">Account Deletion Request</h1>
      <p style="color: #666; margin: 10px 0;">Verification required to proceed</p>
    </div>

    <p>Hello <strong><%= @user.username || @user.email %></strong>,</p>

    <p>We received a request to permanently delete your account. To proceed with this irreversible action, please use the verification code below:</p>

    <div class="otp-code">
      <%= @otp %>
    </div>

    <div class="warning-box">
      <h3 style="color: #dc3545; margin-top: 0;">⚠️ Important Warning</h3>
      <p><strong>This action will permanently:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Delete all your owned projects and their data</li>
        <li>Remove you from all joined projects</li>
        <li>Erase all your personal data and settings</li>
        <li>Cancel all pending join requests</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>This cannot be undone!</strong></p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Security Information:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>This code expires in <strong><%= @expires_in %> minutes</strong></li>
      <li>Do not share this code with anyone</li>
      <li>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email and secure your account</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you did not request account deletion, please contact our support team immediately.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated security email from Your App</p>
      <p>If you have questions, contact us at security@yourapp.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>